267
00:17:50.872 --> 00:17:52.574
Tonight.

268
00:17:52.607 --> 00:17:54.374
Lisa. Go get your mama.

269
00:17:57.277 --> 00:18:00.247
<i>Y'all gon' have food.</i>
<i>drink. music.</i>

270
00:18:00.280 --> 00:18:02.115
