427
00:25:53.621 --> 00:25:55.089
Club Juke.

428
00:25:55.122 --> 00:25:57.625
We gon' have us
a battle of the blues.

429
00:25:59.026 --> 00:26:01.028
It's gon' be
a real ring-a-ding-ding.

430
00:26:01.062 --> 00:26:02.229
